  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0cm 5.75pt 0cm 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Napoar were long ago a race of humanoid aliens. =
Before
  being a space faring race they were able to foresee a massive climate
  changing event to their home world. The Napoar had not developed the abil=
ity to
  travel between the stars, instead they were able to progress their techno=
logy
  so far that they were able to transfer their consciousness in to cybernet=
ic
  bodies. <br>
  <br>
  The Napoar developed bodies were extremely hardy and able to withstand
  extreme heat and weather to survive the massive change to their home worl=
d. <br>
  <br>
  In transcending to this synthetic state the Napoar lost many of the evolu=
tion
  developed emotional instinctual behaviours. They were no longer driven by=
 a
  will to seek power and have lost their aggression. <br>
  <br>
  The Napoar find non aggressive races to be far more agreeable and seek for
  every race in the Galaxy to find their own place and to coexist and help =
each
  other survive. They see no reason why war or conflict is needed at all.</=
p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Napoar prefer Fighters / Missile Bombers combine=
d with
  Missiles on smaller designs, with a Balanced approach to Energy Research.=
</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><i style=3D'mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>In game term=
s this race
  can be one of the fastest to spread to other planets. Because of their new
  bodies they find it easy to develop the technology to populate different
  types of worlds. They are extremely passive though and are not the best at
  war. They will attempt to live in coexistence with other peaceful races.<=
o:p></o:p></i></p>
